# generated by `theme build` — do not edit
# Only the 16-color ANSI palette is themed here. The window chrome (background,
# foreground, cursor, selection) is left to ghostty's own theme directive
# (`theme = Ghostty Default Style Dark` in ~/.config/ghostty/config) so the
# macOS dark default stays. Programs that emit ANSI colors (ls --color, git
# diff, etc.) still follow the active theme via the palette overrides below.
